{"tid":979942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深水埗洗太平地　警大舉掃場","createTime":"2019-01-13T06:27:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T09:29:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e2c000ca94bccb218a17ac7081b0b14dfb9842c8","tid":979942,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T06:27:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190113/20589931\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190113%2F20589931&d=cNQCUWuAuUgGHXOevH1H0I9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=6dd81345\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190113%2F20589931&h=9879243f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190113/20589931</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月13日 <br />\n<br />\n深水埗洗太平地　警大舉掃場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190113/large/13la5p70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190113%2Flarge%2F13la5p70.jpg&h=dadcac67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員在街頭行動，場面大陣仗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】年近歲晚，警方有見本港黑幫近期活動頻繁，接連發生燒車、傷人等腥風血雨案件，為打擊黑幫氣燄，近日進行多次高調拘捕行動，昨晚又動員包括反黑組近50名警員，到深水埗一帶查牌「洗太平地」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n引來市民注目<br />\n<br />\n查牌行動由約25名西九龍警區反黑組便衣探員，聯同約25名機動部隊（PTU）軍裝警員進行，昨晚8時半展開，警方於深水埗元州街出發，首先進入一間遊戲機中心查牌，要求在場人士拿出身份證供查閱，了解有否可疑人士及通緝犯。約50名警員全部進入舖位行動，其後警員移師至一間酒吧查牌，亦未有發現。<br />\n<br />\n警方最後帶隊到青山道一間麻雀館查牌，警員魚貫進入麻雀館，要求在場人士安靜，並逐一查眾人身份，又記錄部份人士的資料。整個查牌行動過程順利，三間場所在場人士均表現合作，大批警員在街頭行動，場面高調，行動期間引來市民注目。行動約30分鐘後完結，在場警員未有回應交代行動目的，行動中未有帶走任何人。<br />\n<br />\n■記者姜偉康  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n蒙面賊爆錢幣店　盜民初紙幣"},{"pid":"bbc652e3eee48d45712afa61ae7c21f5e44376bf","tid":979942,"uid":29540,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T06:30:15.000Z","msg":"西面madam<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae03a4c96c523819a60bc0ebf52b55777a669d88","tid":979942,"uid":16676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T06:44:46.000Z","msg":"一年查一次<br />\n30分鐘, 3間收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c10de5da2c77039b15ea19b93ad18b8267a8ffd9","tid":979942,"uid":19141,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T06:58:28.000Z","msg":"仲以為係去掃南亞賊<br />\n咁大班人剩係去機鋪查身份證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53134a3b4dc985c5f12cba64b38713d649ca9ead","tid":979942,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T07:26:09.000Z","msg":"黑幫自己洗完太平地再等警方黎做大龍鳳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b889c4cd6350874bb832651505aaf51711fbb25f","tid":979942,"uid":45353,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T09:02:24.000Z","msg":"深水埗街市果頭d南亞明顯黑底<br />\n有無check先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a733a51081819c329a3e8d63b669bca99cdad21","tid":979942,"uid":128600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b889c4cd6350874bb832651505aaf51711fbb25f","tid":979942,"uid":45353,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T09:02:24.000Z","msg":"深水埗街市果頭d南亞明顯黑底<br />\n有無check先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T09:06:37.000Z","msg":"食環洗地都會通知聲"},{"pid":"e676cab0cc210eb4d9e9f59ad8ca9c87d946d0e7","tid":979942,"uid":154763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T09:06:47.000Z","msg":"點解唔掃天橋底斑道友"},{"pid":"62527b8df772ac600e3c91a5f6547fcdf23553e5","tid":979942,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T09:25:06.000Z","msg":"查身分證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成班差佬都係廢柴"},{"pid":"8ec3a5937fdc7cd1781a05010c593b2d3b65c78e","tid":979942,"uid":63950,"like":0,"d